vote.title: An ordinance granting renewal of a revocable license to Big Outdoor Texas, LLC for the use of approximately 149 square feet of aerial space to occupy, maintain and utilize the existing videoboard sign over a portion of Field Street right-of-way located near its intersection with Elm Street - Revenue: General Fund $1,227.00 annually, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
